 Gloria Olorunto aka Maraji, a popular Instagram comedienne, surprised fans a few days ago when she announced that she is expecting her first child. The comedienne, who had been off social media for 12 weeks, has now uploaded a lengthy video detailing how she underwent a severe Hemorrhoid operation earlier this year, married her Ghana-based partner privately, and conceived almost immediately. READ ALSO: Comedienne Maraji Reveals She’s Expecting First Child She said: “In the beginning of the year I had a hemorrhoid surgery done. I took a break before, during and after it….the recovery process was hard….because mine was worst….” About her private wedding she said: “We just wanted to do it and get married, it was quick, it was within a month, small wedding in a sitting room, my family and his, then shortly after i got pregnant which is crazy because I have PCOS…we were surprised because we had sex just like twice when i got pregnant” Watch video below:  